Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.43,0:00:09.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,The countless flowers,\Nenveloped in light...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.51,0:00:19.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,...gaze at tomorrow\Nwith unwavering eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.00,0:00:38.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,Everyone wishes for me to be pure...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.27,0:00:46.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,...but what can I bring\Nwith me to the frayed skies?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.48,0:00:53.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,What I've made my own\Nby breaking off flowers in bloom...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.85,0:00:59.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,All such sinful things...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.29,0:01:06.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why did I stop making\Npromises with the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.73,0:01:13.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because even if I try\Nto run far from all the pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.00,0:01:20.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,...a cold wind rustles\Nmy hair... Don't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.71,0:01:27.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,Where can I ever find the answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.87,0:02:16.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.10,0:02:19.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,You just said,\N"This will be easy," didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.04,0:02:28.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,That fool...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.45,0:02:32.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Simile Simoun\Nis a Simoun prototype...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.62,0:02:36.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,It hasn't received\Nthe grace of Tempus Spatium.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.55,0:02:39.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,It can't draw a Ri Majon wake.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.32,0:02:47.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Blue Spring
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.17,0:02:55.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,Such beautiful lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.31,0:02:59.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,Watch closely. M? U isn't just practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.14,0:03:04.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because it'll be your souls and\Nbodies that control the Simouns' flight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.71,0:03:08.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Elly, why are\Nyou dressed like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.69,0:03:16.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is the last time I'll ever\Nsee anything as beautiful as this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.20,0:03:24.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's the emerald pattern...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.64,0:03:30.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.64,0:03:34.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's she thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.01,0:03:36.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,She's crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.25,0:03:43.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,Does this look like a real Simoun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.27,0:03:58.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,Where did you find her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.17,0:03:59.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,She enlisted.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.94,0:04:03.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,Enlisted? That's hard to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.37,0:04:10.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Who'd volunteer at a time like this,\Nknowing they'd have to go into battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.20,0:04:28.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.16,0:04:59.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are you in Tempest too?\NNobody else joined the battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.43,0:05:00.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,I was alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.93,0:05:02.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,What were you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.27,0:05:03.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,What were you thinking?\NBut I was alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.97,0:05:07.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,Simulating the Emerald\NRi Majon of all things.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.50,0:05:11.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,How would that make\NNeviril feel if she saw it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.37,0:05:13.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,Was I doing a Ri Majon?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.18,0:05:16.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,Who's Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.81,0:05:21.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,When Simoun sibyllae take to the\Nskies, it's called praying to the skies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.09,0:05:25.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,Make sure you never\Nuse the word battle again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.83,0:05:33.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,So who's Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.46,0:05:36.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril is the regina of Chor Tempest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.57,0:05:41.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Aurea, the Golden Priestess!\NI want to pair up with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.74,0:05:43.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.27,0:05:46.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why not?\NShe's the top Simoun rider, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.48,0:05:48.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,Simoun rider...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.75,0:05:50.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah, till now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.91,0:05:53.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,But it might not be true anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.22,0:05:58.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because you're amazing!\NI think I really like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.19,0:06:01.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, why don't you pair up with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.19,0:06:03.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,Listen, where's this Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.66,0:06:40.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,It brings back memories.\NWhen we were trainees...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.30,0:06:44.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,...nothing made me happier\Nthan waiting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.57,0:06:47.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,That hasn't changed one bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.20,0:06:50.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dressed like that...\Nyou're leaving the ship too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.51,0:06:54.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes. Since it's been a long\Ntime since my 17th birthday...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.08,0:07:00.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,I've decided to go to the Spring.\NAnd I have one last favor to ask...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.32,0:07:01.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.72,0:07:05.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.96,0:07:09.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,...of going to the Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.66,0:07:11.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,If you don't mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.97,0:07:20.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,Of course, Elly.\NI will accompany you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.70,0:07:24.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril! Anyone seen Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.18,0:07:26.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,Have you seen Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.98,0:07:30.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,Stop calling her that. Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.58,0:07:32.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,...um, Aer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.68,0:07:36.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is Chor Tempest's\Nmaintenance hangar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.45,0:07:38.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,Where's Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.39,0:07:40.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,You here, Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.02,0:07:44.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is the cafeteria.\NAnd this is the ballroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.76,0:07:46.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,Where's Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.90,0:07:55.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.17,0:07:57.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is the forward deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.87,0:08:00.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril, what's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.91,0:08:03.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,Elly said she's going to the Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.28,0:08:07.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,She's unpaired at the moment,\Nso I'm accompanying her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.58,0:08:10.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're lying.\NThen why are you taking luggage?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.55,0:08:14.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,I haven't made up my mind yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.99,0:08:21.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,So there's a chance that\NI might enter the Spring as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.10,0:08:23.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,If so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.17,0:08:25.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,But you can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.34,0:08:28.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,You can't do that!\NBecause if you enter the Spring...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.84,0:08:32.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,...that means you'll have Tempus\NSpatium choose your gender, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.08,0:08:35.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.65,0:08:37.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.15,0:08:40.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer. Chor Tempest Simoun sibylla.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.98,0:08:43.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'd like to pair up with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.15,0:08:47.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,Those who are neither male\Nnor female can fly Simouns.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.19,0:08:49.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,Now's our only chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.06,0:08:53.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yet if you go to the Spring,\Nyou can't be my pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.33,0:08:57.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,She couldn't to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.53,0:09:02.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,My 17th birthday\Npassed over a year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.54,0:09:05.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're an exceptional Simoun sibylla...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.61,0:09:10.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and in this state of emergency,\Nthe nation can't afford to lose you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.38,0:09:14.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,So Onasia has agreed not\Nto summon you to the Spring...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.22,0:09:16.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please, Paraietta.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.45,0:09:17.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let me go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.22,0:09:22.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.17,0:09:32.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,We are all born as females.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.34,0:09:38.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,But to create a society,\Nhalf the population must be male.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.57,0:09:42.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,Tempus Spatium has decreed\Nthe world should be so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.81,0:09:48.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Once we've turned 17, we're allowed\Nto choose our permanent gender.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.25,0:09:53.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,But in the case of Simoun sibyllae,\Nthis can be delayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.02,0:09:58.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,Our nation, Kyuukoku, has gotten\Ninvaded by countless countries.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.40,0:10:02.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,Our only hope of battling\Nthem are Simouns...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.70,0:10:06.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and you sibyllae,\Nwho can talk with the Simouns.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.17,0:10:11.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,If you wish, you may delay\Nyour pilgrimage to the Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.87,0:10:17.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,If, on the other hand, you yearn for\Nthe Spring, we cannot stop you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.18,0:10:19.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,Especially Chor Tempest...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.98,0:10:25.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,Since the war began, you and Chor\NCaput have suffered great losses.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.56,0:10:31.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,Those who've turned 17 are free\Nto choose the same path as Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.73,0:10:33.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,There's no way I would.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.73,0:10:38.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,Man or woman, I haven't\Ndecided yet. I don't even want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.17,0:10:42.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,As long as I'm in battle with a Simoun,\NI won't have to go to the Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.64,0:10:46.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's why I came here.\NAre you guys different?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.38,0:10:50.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,No question.\NOnce you're of age, you have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.68,0:10:53.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,It means you're going\Nto become an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.88,0:10:58.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,But right now, the nation\Nneeds our powers, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.25,0:11:00.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh? Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.66,0:11:05.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then you've all already decided\Nto become a man or woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.26,0:11:09.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Have you, Big Sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.19,0:11:31.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,Listen, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.49,0:11:33.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's fine, Elly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.72,0:11:37.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,One last time...\NWon't you pair up with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.13,0:11:41.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want you to see me fly as\Nan auriga to the great temple below.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.83,0:11:47.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then I'll have them\Nget a Simoun ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.94,0:11:57.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well? How's my driving?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.45,0:12:00.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,Not "driving,"\N"speaking with the Simoun."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.22,0:12:02.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry. I'm just so psyched.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.99,0:12:06.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because this is the first time\NI've touched a real Simoun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.79,0:12:08.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,First time?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.03,0:12:13.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,I've always wanted to ride one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.06,0:12:14.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,I've always wanted to ride one.\NReally?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.43,0:12:16.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,You know what I mean, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.07,0:12:19.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,Everything has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.74,0:12:23.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because you're not "praying to\Nthe skies" for Tempus Spatium...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.97,0:12:26.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,...but for war?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.58,0:12:27.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.98,0:12:29.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,There's no difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.61,0:12:32.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,You don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.22,0:12:38.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,What kind...\NWhat kind of place the battlefield is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.29,0:12:45.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,I do. Because I trained\Non the front lines in the south.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.70,0:12:52.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,Before the war, sibyllae would go to\Nthe Spring when they turned 17, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.20,0:12:53.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.67,0:12:59.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,But now, the great temple's laws\Nsay we don't have to go to the Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.44,0:13:03.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,As long as we're winning this war...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.55,0:13:13.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Aer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.90,0:13:22.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,How rude. She's an auriga, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.67,0:13:23.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.83,0:13:28.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,So she made you fly as her sagitta?\NThe finest auriga in the nation?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.02,0:13:45.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,Out of all of us here, is Paraietta\Nthe only one who's turned 17?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.99,0:13:50.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,Big Sister, you'll be\N17 next month, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.10,0:13:57.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,Either way, we all will be soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.70,0:14:02.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aren't you going after Neviril?\NYou're going to become a man for her...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.47,0:14:05.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,You made\Nthat decision long ago, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.01,0:14:10.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,I still feel that there are things\NI need to accomplish here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.28,0:14:50.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,Elly, have you decided?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.92,0:14:54.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,Which gender you'll\Nchoose at the Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.06,0:15:00.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Um, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.46,0:15:02.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.53,0:15:07.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,I've always been female, so I think\Nit'd be more natural to stay one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.57,0:15:10.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,I might also want to become a male.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.54,0:15:15.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,After all, there aren't a lot of job\Nopportunities unless you're a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.18,0:15:23.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,I know you must be weary,\NSimoun sibylla, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.92,0:15:26.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.22,0:15:32.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,Simoun sibylla...\NSuch a beautiful sight...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.90,0:15:37.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,O priestess, please guide\Nour nation to the righteous path.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.67,0:15:39.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please protect us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.75,0:15:53.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are you Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.58,0:15:54.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.02,0:16:05.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,If I'm with you,\NI think I'll have fun flying.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.97,0:16:48.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,O sibyllae...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.90,0:16:54.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,We are overjoyed to know that\Nyour time for prayer is now over.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.24,0:17:00.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,We thank you for having\Nprotected us all thus far...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.89,0:17:39.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.99,0:17:43.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm supposed to think\N"male" or "female" in my head...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.63,0:17:47.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,...but what happens if I think of both?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.60,0:17:50.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,You'll be fine.\NThere's nothing to worry about, Elly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.94,0:17:55.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,Onasia...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.18,0:18:03.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,Great Priestess Onasia...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.48,0:18:10.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,Forgive me for not journeying here\Nthough my 17th birthday is long past.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.09,0:18:14.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Elly, enter the Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.89,0:18:17.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,And offer a prayer...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.77,0:19:01.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.54,0:19:04.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,What should I do? I can't decide!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.02,0:19:28.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,The holy sounds of Tempus Spatium\Nhave just been bestowed upon you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.58,0:19:46.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,I was told that starting\Ntoday, my name is Eliph.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.85,0:19:48.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.92,0:19:51.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.55,0:19:55.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,They say your voice\Nchanges overtime...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.26,0:19:59.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and your chest gets smaller, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.16,0:20:04.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,Nothing's really changed, has it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.90,0:20:06.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.34,0:20:09.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,Nothing has changed, Eliph.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.41,0:20:45.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, Sibylla Roatreamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.91,0:20:48.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're staying too, my lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.34,0:20:53.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,I grew up being told\NI should become a sibylla...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.45,0:20:56.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,...so if I went home now,\Nthey'd yell at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.25,0:21:00.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,We all have one, don't we? A reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.37,0:21:18.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,The thing is...\NI can't fly this alone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.77,0:21:51.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,You didn't go to the Spring?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.04,0:21:55.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,I did go. But I decided not to enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.42,0:22:07.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Higher.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.79,0:22:10.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,Than our ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.16,0:22:12.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,Higher.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.13,0:22:14.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.86,0:22:47.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,It is played by my wounds...\Nthe song of prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.60,0:22:51.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let it ring out over\Nthe grieving universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.83,0:22:58.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,Can we change tomorrow?\NDon't be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.91,0:23:06.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want to let you know\Nhow my heart's overflowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.29,0:23:19.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,"I want to get closer to you."\N"I want to feel your pulse."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.39,0:23:24.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,I was too defiant,\Nand I took the long way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.53,0:23:28.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,The blue moon is swaying silently.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.57,0:23:32.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,My true heart's desire is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.57,0:23:38.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can't reach you.\NMy tears of pain trickle down.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.45,0:23:43.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,Soar away into the sky, song of prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.99,0:23:47.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,Carrying my love that came too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.42,0:23:52.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,What can I do to change tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.10,0:23:59.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just hold on to "now" the way it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.94,0:24:06.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,To Be Continued
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.31,0:24:11.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,Shoukoku's massive long-range cannons are\Nheaded this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.35,0:24:15.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,Next time on Simoun...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.12,0:24:16.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Distant War\NNext time on Simoun...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.59,0:24:19.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Distant War\NThe Distant War.
